{"tid":2347872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌新式的士個設計簡直反智","createTime":"2020-12-31T10:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T11:01:02.000Z","uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"73dd852e6097592f92a6c3e20a8448b6e40a830e","tid":2347872,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"新嗰隻的士隻門唔係自己關，要等個司機㩒掣慢慢關<br />\n<br />\n話說我今日咁啱覆診，截到呢隻的士<br />\n<br />\n我一坐低，度門中門大開，我就同個司機大佬講：「師傅唔該青松觀路15號。」<br />\n司機把聲本身就大，問：「即係邊度呀。」<br />\n呢個時候隻門先響，開始關緊<br />\n我咪細聲講：「屯門。」<br />\n司機話：「我夠知屯門，你講個門牌我點知邊度。」<br />\n於是我死死地氣：「青山醫院。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候度門仲有一半，出面個麻甩佬聽到掩住半邊咀響度笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻設計都唔顧人地私隱，正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5225a6071ad31d6742fc1c1d48f435d84eb9a59a","tid":2347872,"uid":87043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"唔call uber ?"},{"pid":"d62af586106e3a7e51f660b8108c918f84fc393c","tid":2347872,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5225a6071ad31d6742fc1c1d48f435d84eb9a59a","tid":2347872,"uid":87043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"唔call uber ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:54:38.000Z","msg":"嗰下見有車又費事等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406d93a81e46fd607b35f5d044177da5a904c6cc","tid":2347872,"uid":87043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"其實冇人留意你去邊<br />\n唔好咁睇重自己<br />\n少啲介意人地點睇 <br />\n你會開心好多 <br />\n2022 又係好開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cba18f54af71d50d719c0259b5262f72